PORTFOLIO

SPC Dashboard

The project is to create an interactive, data-driven dashboard for statistical process control (SPC), enabling the manufacturing quality team to visualize, monitor, and analyze measurement data in real time. This solution will help detect process issues early, ensure product compliance with customer specifications, and drive continuous process improvement.

ABOUT ME

I'm a results-driven Project Manager, Project Engineer, and Data Analyst with a passion for solving problems through both strategic leadership and data-driven decision-making. With a background in engineering and experience leading cross-functional projects from concept to execution, I bring a unique combination of technical expertise, operational insight, and analytical skills. I thrive in dynamic environments where I can bridge the gap between technical teams and business goals.

As a Project Engineer, I have worked on multiple Software integration projects across EU specialized in Metal packaging. As a Project Manager, I coordinated and delivered 10+ projects focused on semi-automatic industrial machines and assembly lines. As Data Analyst, I have built interactive dashboards to drive process improvement.
